function refreshmachine(machs, auxparams, handleDelayLoad, dotmachs ) {
var machineparams = '';
var dotmachineparams = '';
var id = getFormElementViaFormName('main_form', 'id').value;
id = isValEmpty( id ) ? '' : '&id='+id;
var machines = new Object();
var auxparamfields = new Array();
var auxparamvalues = new Array();
machines['usernotes'] = 'usernotes';

machines['systemnotes'] = 'systemnotes';

if (machs != null) {
var targetmachines = machs.split(String.fromCharCode(5));
for (var i = 0; i < targetmachines.length; i++) {
if ( machines[targetmachines[i]] != null ) {
if ( handleDelayLoad && eval( 'window.' + machines[targetmachines[i]] + '_machine' ) != null ) {
eval( 'window.' + machines[targetmachines[i]] + '_machine' ).buildtable( );
if (document.forms.main_form.elements[machines[targetmachines[i]] +'loaded'] != null) document.forms.main_form.elements[machines[targetmachines[i]] +'loaded'].value = 'T';
}
else {
machineparams += '&machine='+targetmachines[i];
if (!isValEmpty(auxparamfields[targetmachines[i]])) auxparams = (!isValEmpty(auxparams) ? auxparams + '&' : '')+auxparamfields[targetmachines[i]]+'='+auxparamvalues[targetmachines[i]];
}
}
}
}
 if (dotmachs != null) {
targetmachines = dotmachs.split(String.fromCharCode(5));
for (var i = 0; i < targetmachines.length; i++) {
if ( machines[targetmachines[i]] != null ) {
dotmachineparams += '&dotmachine='+targetmachines[i];
if (!isValEmpty(auxparamfields[targetmachines[i]])) auxparams = (!isValEmpty(auxparams) ? auxparams + '&' : '')+auxparamfields[targetmachines[i]]+'='+auxparamvalues[targetmachines[i]];
}
}
}
if ( isValEmpty(machineparams) && isValEmpty(dotmachineparams) ) 
return;
NS.form.setInited(false);
document.getElementById('server_commands').contentWindow.location.replace('\/app\/common\/custom\/custrecordentry.nl?cf=89\x26rectype=396\x26r=T'+id+machineparams+dotmachineparams+(isValEmpty(auxparams) ? '' : '&'+auxparams)+ '&ts=' + new Date().getTime());
}
function showmachine(mname,shown) {
if (shown && NLTabIsDisplayNone(mname)) return;
document.getElementById(mname+'_layer').style.display = shown ? '' : 'none';
NLDisplaySubTab(mname, shown);
if (shown && document.forms.main_form.elements[mname+'loaded'] != null && document.forms.main_form.elements[mname+'loaded'].value=='F') refreshmachine( mname, null, true );
document.getElementById(mname+'ltidot').src = shown ? '/images/forms/tab/contentindicator_on.png': '/images/forms/tab/contentindicator_off.png';
   if (typeof onShowMachineTab == "function")
      onShowMachineTab(mname,shown);
}
function NLDisplaySubTab(tname,shown) {
  var tab  = document.getElementById(tname+'lnk');
  tab.className = shown ? 'formsubtabon':'formsubtaboff';
document.getElementById(tname+'txt').className = shown ? 'formsubtabtext formsubtabtexton':'formsubtabtext formsubtabtextoff';
if (shown && typeof NetSuite!='undefined' && NetSuite.RTEManager) NetSuite.RTEManager.resyncSizeAll();
} 

function NLTabIsDisplayNone(tname) {
  var tab  = document.getElementById(tname+'lnk');
  return tab && tab.style.display == 'none';
}

function CollapsenotesMachines(hidden) {
if (NS.form.isInited() && NS.form.isValid()) {
if (!hidden) {
var mnames = '';
if (document.forms.main_form.elements['usernotesloaded'] != null && document.forms.main_form.elements['usernotesloaded'].value=='F')
     mnames += (mnames.length > 0 ? String.fromCharCode(5) : '')+'usernotes';
if (document.forms.main_form.elements['systemnotesloaded'] != null && document.forms.main_form.elements['systemnotesloaded'].value=='F')
     mnames += (mnames.length > 0 ? String.fromCharCode(5) : '')+'systemnotes';
refreshmachine( mnames, null, true );
}
collapsemachine('usernotes',hidden,false);
collapsemachine('systemnotes',hidden,false);
}
}
function hideMachine(mname,hide) {
if (document.getElementById(mname+'_layer') == null) return;
var isHighlighted = (document.getElementById(mname+'lnk') ? document.getElementById(mname+'lnk').className.indexOf('formsubtabon')>=0 : true);
ns_tabUtils.hideTab(mname,hide);
if (!hide && !isHighlighted) {
if (ns_tabUtils.getLayeredTab(mname) && !ns_tabUtils.hasTabVisibleSibling(mname)) {typeof showmachine === 'function' && showmachine(mname,true);} 
else {document.getElementById(mname+'_layer').style.display = 'none';}
return;}
else if (!isHighlighted) return;
if (mname=='usernotes') ShownotesMachine('systemnotes');
else if (mname=='systemnotes') ShownotesMachine('usernotes');
  var loadStatus = document.forms.main_form.elements[mname + 'loaded']
  if (!hide && loadStatus != null && loadStatus.value == 'F') { refreshmachine(mname, null, true); }
}
function NLDisplayTab(tname,shown) {
  var tab  = document.getElementById(tname+'lnk');
  tab.className = shown ? 'formtabon' : 'formtaboff';
  var firstTab = tab.previousSibling.getAttribute('side')=='0';
  var lastTab = tab.nextSibling.getAttribute('side')=='1';
  if (firstTab){ 
    tab.previousSibling.className = shown ? 'formtabseplon' : 'formtabseploff';
    tab.previousSibling.firstChild.className = shown ? 'formtabsepclon' : 'formtabsepcloff';
  } 
  if (lastTab){ 
    tab.nextSibling.className = shown ? 'formtabsepron' : 'formtabseproff';
    tab.nextSibling.firstChild.className = shown ? 'formtabsepcron' : 'formtabsepcroff';
  } 
  document.getElementById(tname+'txt').className = shown ? 'formtabtext formtabtexton':'formtabtext formtabtextoff';
} 


function isTabShown(tname) {
    var tab = NS.jQuery('#'+tname+'_div');
    return !tab.length || (tab.css('display') != 'none');
}

function ShowHideTab(tname,shown) {
    var tabDiv = NS.jQuery('#'+tname+'_div');
    if (!tabDiv.length || tabDiv.css('display') == (shown ? '' : 'none')) return;

    NS.jQuery('#'+tname+'_wrapper').css('display', (shown ? '' : 'none'));

    var machs = allmachs[tname].split(',');
    var mach = vismachs[tname];
    var dotmachs = '';
    if (shown) {
        var i;
        for (i=0;i<machs.length;i++) {
            var dotmach = machs[i];
            if (dotmach != null && dotmach != mach && NS.jQuery('#'+dotmach+'_layer').length && document.forms.main_form.elements[dotmach+'dotted'] != null && document.forms.main_form.elements[dotmach+'dotted'].value=='F')
                dotmachs += (dotmachs.length > 0 ? String.fromCharCode(5) : '') + dotmach;
        }
    }

    tabDiv.css('visibility', '');
    tabDiv.css('display', shown ? '' : 'none');
    NLDisplayTab(tname, shown);
    if (shown && mach != null && NS.jQuery('#'+mach+'_layer').is(":visible") && document.forms.main_form.elements[mach+'loaded'] != null && document.forms.main_form.elements[mach+'loaded'].value=='F')
        refreshmachine(mach, null, true, dotmachs.length > 0 ? dotmachs : null);
    else if (shown && dotmachs.length > 0)
        refreshmachine(null, null, true, dotmachs);
        if(shown) {
            getFormElementViaFormName('main_form', 'selectedtab').value = tname;
        }
    if (shown && (typeof NetSuite != 'undefined') && (typeof NetSuite.RTEManager != 'undefined'))
        NetSuite.RTEManager.resyncSizeAll();
}

function collapsetab(lname,sethidden) {
    expandCollapseTab(lname, sethidden);
}

var sCurrentlySelectedTab = 'notes';
function ShowTab(lname, bIgnoreInited) {

NS.jQuery('.uir_form_tab_container:eq(0)').trigger({
	type: "nsSelect",
	message: "nsSelect fired.",
	time: new Date()
	}, {}
);

if ((bIgnoreInited || NS.form.isInited()) && NS.form.isValid()) {
        if(lname == sCurrentlySelectedTab) return;
        ShowHideTab(lname, true);
        ShowHideTab(sCurrentlySelectedTab, false);
        sCurrentlySelectedTab = lname;
		if (window.NLMachine_clearFocus) {
			NLMachine_clearFocus();
		}
    }
}

    if (NS.form.isInited() && NS.form.isValid()) {
            
            collapsetab('notes', hidden);
    }

(function __showMessagesFromBeforeLoad() {
  try {
    var messages = JSON.parse(nlapiGetFieldValue('custpage__ss_messages_for_client'));
    if (messages && Array.isArray(messages.messages) && typeof require !== 'undefined') {
      require(['N/ui'], function (ui) {
        messages.messages.forEach(function (msg) {
          if (!msg) return;
          ui.message.create(msg).show();
        });
      });
    }
  } catch (e) {
    return;
  }
})();

</script>
